English and Bough's odyssey immediately turns into a farce: the two, disguised as waiters, set fire to a fancy French restaurant and cause chaos as they secretly seek to board Volta's luxury yacht. An attempt to explore Volta's house using virtual glasses ends up in pure anarchy in the real world.
